[SN]TITLE[SN]
Yorkshire bell-ringers 'reject York Minster plea'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The bells of York Minster could remain silent this Christmas after bell-ringers elsewhere reportedly rejected an invitation to ring them.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
16 December 2016 Last updated at 12:57 GMT
York Minster dismissed its 30 volunteer bell-ringers in October after a "safeguarding" issue.
The York Press reported that bell-ringers in Leeds opted to stand by their colleagues and refused York's offer.
